mailSender::addSender()

Description
    public bool mailSender::addSender(string $address [, string $name = ''])
	Adds the address and name pair to the array, $this->from.
	
Parameters
    address
		A string value containing an e-mail address.
    name
		An optional parameter.  A name to associate with the address/name pair.  Default value is ''.
		
Return Values
    Returns TRUE when successful.  Returns FALSE otherwise.
	
See Also
    mailSender::addSubject()
	mailSender::addAttachment()
    mailSender::addBCC()
    mailSender::addBody()
    mailSender::addCC()
    mailSender::addRecipient()
    mailSender::addReplyTo()
	mailSender::addSubject()